OL,6,FReform UK's membership has grown by
OL,7,F50% in the week since Nigel Farage
OL,8,Fdecided to stand as parliamentary
OL,9,Fcandidate, according to figures seen
OL,11,FAlmost 14,000 people have joined
OL,12,FReform in the last seven days - taking
OL,13,Fmembership over 45,000.
