OL,6,FUnlike most political parties, Reform
OL,7,FUK is set up as a limited company.
OL,8,FParty members have no say over policy
OL,9,For in deciding its leaders.
OL,11,FOne of the reasons Mr Sunak is
OL,12,Fbelieved to have called a snap
OL,13,Felection was to catch the Reform party
OL,14,Foff guard.
OL,16,FAnd while the party's membership is
OL,17,Fgrowing, so too are questions about
OL,18,Fsome of its candidates.
