OL,6,FOn Friday the Reform withdrew support
OL,7,Ffor two of its candidates after
OL,8,Fprevious racist comments were
OL,9,Funearthed.
OL,11,FThe party has said it will look into
OL,12,Fother allegations.
OL,14,FNigel Farage told ITV News' Harry
OL,15,FHorton he had 'no idea' why Robert
OL,16,FLomas wasn't campaigning with him -
OL,17,Fbut would look into him allegedly
OL,18,Fsaying that asylum seekers had it 'in
OL,19,Ftheir DNA to lie' and 'black people of
OL,20,FBritain' were 'grifting the race card'
