OL,6,FOne candidate Reform is investigating
OL,7,Fis Robert Lomas, who is standing in
OL,8,FBarnsley North, one of the party's key
OL,9,Ftarget seats.
OL,11,FHe's reported to have said asylum
OL,12,Fseekers had it "in their DNA to lie"
OL,13,Fin comments posted online.
OL,15,FHe also wrote that "Black people of
OL,16,FBritain" were "grifting the race card"
OL,17,Fand should stop acting "like savages",
OL,18,Faccording to The Times.
