OL,6,FAs he campaigned in Barnsley on
OL,7,FTuesday, Mr Farage said he had "no
OL,8,Fidea" why Mr Lomas hadn't appeared
OL,9,Falongside him.
OL,11,FMr Farage said he had only been made
OL,12,Faware of Lomas' comments that morning
OL,13,Fbut said "I'm a little bit alarmed by
OL,14,Fit" and promised to "have a good look
OL,15,Fat it."
OL,17,F"This election's been thrust upon us
OL,18,Fwith almost no time to do vetting, to
OL,19,Fdo any organisation. Of course, we'll
OL,20,Ffind people saying things they
OL,21,Fshouldn't say," he added.
